{
  "_doc": [
    "=== Polaris: Project-level settings (settings.local.json) ===",
    "",
    "This file is gitignored and lives at .claude/settings.local.json in each repo.",
    "It controls permissions for THIS project only.",
    "",
    "Permission model (3 layers, merged at runtime):",
    "  1. ~/.claude/settings.json        — user-level (all projects, all worktrees)",
    "  2. .claude/settings.json           — project-level, committed (team-shared)",
    "  3. .claude/settings.local.json     — project-level, gitignored (personal)",
    "",
    "Sub-agents and worktrees only inherit layer 1 (user-level).",
    "Put general patterns (git, gh, pnpm, Edit, Write) in ~/.claude/settings.json.",
    "Put project-specific patterns here.",
    "",
    "Pattern syntax: Tool(glob_pattern)",
    "  Bash(git *)           — any git command",
    "  Bash(pnpm -C /path *) — pnpm in a specific directory",
    "  Read(/path/**)        — read files under a path",
    "  WebFetch(domain:x.com) — fetch from a specific domain",
    "  mcp__server__tool     — allow a specific MCP tool",
    "",
    "See: https://docs.anthropic.com/en/docs/claude-code/settings"
  ],
  "permissions": {
    "allow": [
      "Skill(update-config)",
      "Skill(update-config:*)",

      "Read(//Users/<USERNAME>/**)",

      "WebFetch(domain:woodpecker.sit.example.com)"
    ],
    "additionalDirectories": [
      "/Users/<USERNAME>/.claude",
      "/Users/<USERNAME>/.claude/projects/-Users-<USERNAME>-work/memory"
    ]
  }
}
